title: Arbitrum DEXs daily transaction volume eclipse Ethereum, Solana
description:
Decentralized exchanges (DEX) transaction volume on Arbitrum, a layer2 network, surpassed that of Ethereum for the first time during the past day, according to DeFillama data. During the reporting period, DEXs on Arbitrum saw their volume soar to $1.843 billion, surpassing Ethereum’s $1.444 billion and Solana’s $683.59 million.
